if st.button("Save"):
    save_customer(name)
```

### 4. Handle Errors Gracefully

```python
try:
    save_customer(name, email)
    st.success("âœ… Customer saved!")
except ValueError as e:
    st.error(f"âŒ Invalid input: {e}")
    st.info("ğŸ’¡ Check email format")
